replies.body: <u></u>you were the leader of Sigma and u seemed like a pretty good pvper. I only played with you since Conquet inc cause you don't show up to scrims. At first you sounded younger than I expected and at times called out in the right place and time. However you seemed to believe that you were better than us, like on foundry I was like go right, and then you only went left, which was infuriating since they were heavy on right. Some times I saw you trying to get into Inlocs team and you acted like a dick. Even after the rounds you said that we all sucked and u are leaving, only to run back when ehlf said we might've gotten into invitationals. That was kinda a scumbag move. If you were to stay I hope to get to know you better and get passed what my original thoughts of you were. How old are you?
